  "title": "Demurrage Analyst | Oil & Gas Trading",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a Trading MNC company, one of the leading players in the Oil & Gas sector. Due to business needs, they are now recruiting a Demurrage Analyst to be part of their team for ongoing transformation projects. They are located in the Central – easily accessible.</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee demurrage exposure for Gasoline desk trade, analyzing and negotiating payables and receivables.</li><li>Prepare demurrage computations and submit timely reports to relevant counterparts.</li><li>Ensure prompt collection of outstanding claims and track incoming funds.</li><li>Collaborate closely with cargo operators for efficient claims file management and documentation.</li><li>Generate weekly/monthly demurrage status reports and handle monthly demurrage accruals.</li><li>Coordinate with the contract desk on purchase and sales contracts, focusing on delivery nomination, Laytime, and demurrage clauses.</li><li>Verify and endorse freight invoices for approval/payment.</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Bachelor’s degree in relevant fields.</li><li>Minimum 1 year of relevant working experience in oil & gas industry.</li><li>Good communication skills and able to work in fast paced environment.</li></ul><p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click <strong>APPLY NOW </strong>or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><ul><li><strong>Email: jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></li><li>RecruitPedia Pte Ltd</li><li>EA License No: 19C9682</li><li>EA Personnel No: R2198636 (Oh Puey Xin)</li></ul>",
